name: The Alternative Board
overview:
Business Coaching - The Alternative Board South Western Connecticut (USA) offers business coaching that help you efficient and effective solution for challenging business problems and offers comprehensive business advice services that help you to conduct your business in optimal manner.

The Alternative Board establishes your own board of advisors and small business mentor. Thousands of business owners of small- and medium-sized companies are members of TAB boards. There are over 140 TAB franchises operating in five countries.

Services Offered:

• Small Business Advisors

• Business Solutions Small Business Strategy Leadership Coaching

• Networking Business Success Stories

• Peer Advisory Board Strategic Business Planning

So do not be late and get solution of your business problem.

For more information please visit http://www.tab-swct.com/
